{
  "meta": {
    "voice": null,
    "language": null,
    "rate": "1",
    "pitch": "0",
    "generatedAt": "2026-03-26T01:07:20.820Z"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ฉันคือใคร และคุณคือใคร – เรียนรู้การพูดเกี่ยวกับคน",
      "file": "th-th-66fb9e9f6f7dfb3c0a239e46710566e0012a0969.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Who I Am and Who You Are – Learning to Talk About People",
      "file": "en-us-f2ea1a54488b4a48dc2cbf6b91d3c04382615b2d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "บทนำ",
      "file": "th-th-861e85f4c23d7d531e15db3e028210fd28a78bbf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "file": "en-us-ddc4642e5ae6a7ebd9c4918c52a19699a895de75.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ในบทเรียนนี้ เราจะเรียนรู้การพูดว่าเราเป็นใคร และพูดถึงคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-ccc13a0ebd48ffdfe22ab99e6f920321875c1bb5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "In this lesson, we will learn how to say who we are and talk about other people.",
      "file": "en-us-b6af15c3cfd0b933504bbf79cfdfdd709eca500e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เราจะใช้ประโยคง่าย ๆ เพื่อบอกชื่อ และบอกความรู้สึก",
      "file": "th-th-3af2f902123ec6ec879baa195f368cccb0bb8328.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We will use simple sentences to say names and how someone feels.",
      "file": "en-us-6bf14654520033b18e711d4e0ea2ce70481bfe4d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "และเราจะจำสิ่งสำคัญอย่างหนึ่ง: พระเจ้ารู้จักทุกคนตามชื่อ",
      "file": "th-th-899580f0a2d709bfe2c17996692ed3ec9ad92843.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "And we will remember something very important: God knows every person by name.",
      "file": "en-us-c5e07b9eae9501364dd915bfef24420f902b1f64.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "1. การพูดเกี่ยวกับตัวเอง",
      "file": "th-th-05a7183bdda57947f2ddd8d6ac7afbce69439fb3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "1. Talking about myself",
      "file": "en-us-a12dd7491ae90321b1220517c54e88dab184ce4c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เมื่อเราพูดเกี่ยวกับตัวเอง เราใช้รูปแบบพิเศษ",
      "file": "th-th-05f3d3cc127651eb78d82cb14b091cf3aea2d33a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "When we talk about ourselves, we use a special form.",
      "file": "en-us-2b073f31ab8f554a23194d067e8190b3460be9d2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เราสามารถบอกชื่อหรือบอกว่าเรารู้สึกอย่างไร",
      "file": "th-th-edbcbc02513b3e27b9b6a6cdc190e2c523c5e340.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "With this form, we can say our name or how we feel.",
      "file": "en-us-21d937c6431cd161d398e80bb46317d34e9515be.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2ea7a194959761fc6819b0a71918a66db527430d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am happy.",
      "file": "en-us-23939b7341e0b2db15f437958c508b0842216b70.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-5fd7218dba7b66e228565abe8c016114d4e7ab2c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ประโยคเหล่านี้คือการพูดถึงตัวเอง",
      "file": "th-th-6ec3591a799402f9fe4f26c3fd21b4b0bdd552c5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, the person is talking about themselves.",
      "file": "en-us-3023e093dcdaebf3a43c56e61b732c66ca4f626c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับคำว่า “ฉัน”",
      "file": "th-th-e4e0d392df3d2552a9bd0c63b7f67317e8112e0b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like saying: I.",
      "file": "en-us-886701a3763ebd3826fb24852f45cee37606ec44.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "2. การพูดกับคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-a26b5774ea976ad690df4546ab2054fb26795a79.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "2. Talking to another person",
      "file": "en-us-18851b1a8429e91fbb743e94437439b812127fe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เมื่อเราพูดกับคนอื่นโดยตรง เราใช้รูปแบบอีกแบบหนึ่ง",
      "file": "th-th-8ac48b985819fc8f6c8f453dd39d744a7f7b85d5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "When we speak directly to someone, we use another form.",
      "file": "en-us-97dccd3ca5536ea19c2d1123deab58e4a4e30238.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เราใช้เมื่อเรามองไปที่คนคนนั้นและพูดกับเขา",
      "file": "th-th-670519f35bc851ab2756be64afaeaa2ea134e557.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We use it when we look at the person and talk to them.",
      "file": "en-us-d284a9a1e59e44832f0ff7927fc0e9d6c7558dc8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-d77d87e8e23a7d0f9fa4de519606bdb500208fe4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-4057e5dd51af2766d75664e2de122f5da27990c9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d88c326c1e116ceabac6175587976a0f555d96a0.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "นี่คือการพูดกับคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-dcd7f9e0456e93d63fe0d42a92034a492deb86de.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking to someone.",
      "file": "en-us-d67882b8c8d9a58856e17377cff5b3a32e37cefa.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับคำว่า “คุณ”",
      "file": "th-th-ba2cd1937c40fc0db0a5e8896b33c1fd48c258ba.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like saying: you.",
      "file": "en-us-8d3f124aa46d0eacf90373812fa4e630b0945598.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "3. การพูดถึงเด็กผู้ชายหรือผู้ชาย",
      "file": "th-th-f3b1ecd97b337e7aaa87a207fa5a04d933aed89d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "3. Talking about a boy or a man",
      "file": "en-us-63b52f4d13ad9a0caeca42af488f47e605a28ce6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตอนนี้ ลองนึกถึงเด็กผู้ชายที่ไม่ได้อยู่ในการสนทนา",
      "file": "th-th-0575a7fe0b9834c003e792e92a866adccc5ba959.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Now, imagine we are talking about a boy who is not in the conversation.",
      "file": "en-us-ca663d0193008c55159b8b72539a768b90acc626.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เขาไม่ได้พูด และเราไม่ได้พูดกับเขาโดยตรง",
      "file": "th-th-b2780ce55d0f87b0fd8bb1816d4f21127556805e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is not speaking and we are not talking to him directly.",
      "file": "en-us-f27c9ee328afc273b74c52e55a6f97450a18a316.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรากำลังพูดเกี่ยวกับเขาให้คนอื่นฟัง",
      "file": "th-th-9137735d01d1d829faa3840a5c809b492dbda758.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are just talking about him to another person.",
      "file": "en-us-aef94edf5f9a2ce28315c2a91b174d18ab866aef.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2a2632a545de1823da43afd6efaf7a9bdde88adf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-82d5659b428ca8187f1b62cd7b1c594773f693e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-1875dbfb2e551e944cb3613e86530d6cc03308b8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "นี่คือการพูดถึงเด็กผู้ชายหรือผู้ชาย",
      "file": "th-th-ce90424642daf7ccd706bdc5b2538e332c25111c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking about a boy or a man.",
      "file": "en-us-d2446f94cd5c8e99c31d773be4ec137f3eccb813.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับการชี้ไปที่เขาแล้วบอก",
      "file": "th-th-191b94e0bdc01878198d0dd329d844f16dd5e4b7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like pointing to him and telling something.",
      "file": "en-us-971f789f9248667ff5601c4b451a23ca5a4a4768.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "4. การพูดถึงเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิง",
      "file": "th-th-6f2eeb6b5560ad31bab5a1cbdffcdfa57b08bba1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "4. Talking about a girl or a woman",
      "file": "en-us-2928311111f0c8234c4ed787b45727aa6b7eb9d9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรายังสามารถพูดถึงเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิงได้",
      "file": "th-th-91d744cc573d506a274bcaa1bb2e5e4f92c3501b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We can also talk about a girl or a woman.",
      "file": "en-us-97cd6fc43619a005ee07d6e18e29bb750214923b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนเดิม เธอไม่ได้พูด และเราไม่ได้พูดกับเธอโดยตรง",
      "file": "th-th-490ae696b6b02bc68a214bf97402171a9811b75c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Just like before, she is not speaking and we are not talking to her directly.",
      "file": "en-us-bca256274bf143b543da2a19a681bce2f5883c73.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรากำลังพูดเกี่ยวกับเธอ",
      "file": "th-th-c8d4f916b541a7b4a4f474e0e53edd9902924224.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are talking about her.",
      "file": "en-us-cea4656f37534286c5381eff9c3d315ce221a0ed.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-30ddae33c2bccaca73a4be47e7712fd4c9bfcf94.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d1b3d3c880ee376906cd771d820b9756e0aed280.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is Hannah.",
      "file": "en-us-d1fcfedd52306f6c11995ac3e30ad2bbc7bf56f6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "นี่คือการพูดถึงเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิง",
      "file": "th-th-44f0c82f6f568c5baec32fe28bc3b2f46adf0e6c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking about a girl or a woman.",
      "file": "en-us-557338fd540294c4f62a0380eab0bb726cf1dad4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับการชี้ไปที่เธอแล้วบอก",
      "file": "th-th-2f17e8715e4167d0db2411dca497cdd36e8050b9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like pointing to her and telling something.",
      "file": "en-us-7282ef6dddf24ea6c25c3b292a99e552f4eff020.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "5. พระเจ้ารู้จักคุณ",
      "file": "th-th-3701743463ab796a62dad039c82c1c9fc9453d73.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "5. God knows you",
      "file": "en-us-0df08ba78ecc3cc8c934c02a47dde7b40dd1c956.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "พระเจ้ารู้จักทุกคนตามชื่อ",
      "file": "th-th-676e9faba64dc76b753c9da08bc48b6b8de36333.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God knows every person by name.",
      "file": "en-us-bcef82b34bc452f2185c10145f2180c2cf749014.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "คุณมีค่าและพิเศษมาก",
      "file": "th-th-f96b79fbeca224b3f750782091fd2eb59b7137f6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are important and special.",
      "file": "en-us-2a95145c0656668a301ed7aa59c259a140977cdd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am special.",
      "file": "en-us-30659168470ea344e663e832d4071108350f3afd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is special.",
      "file": "en-us-16532c2721b9ac71a837d574e6544ce38cdaa297.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is special.",
      "file": "en-us-5c8404f35b519d351ea9495b1ec21edc456b1f43.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ทุกคนล้วนพิเศษ",
      "file": "th-th-f7cf98c0f2872aac8e8255e1743c7b213efbbbc5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "All people are special.",
      "file": "en-us-3bf1c88b4de9057ee558e9c39d9aa19d5ce28396.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "พระเจ้ารู้จักทุกคน",
      "file": "th-th-22879598fbea37566cfa2420c4c65f6d47ad6c22.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God knows each one of them.",
      "file": "en-us-2b0df657ba37a2492b85992db8f6ff1dc9bc254d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "สรุป",
      "file": "th-th-e2104abbb24d4358d36bb7b03403a362d1cc4e9a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Conclusion",
      "file": "en-us-e1f195b655ae7e4263baa0a54dd91effd6a06a28.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ในบทเรียนนี้ เราเรียนรู้การพูดเกี่ยวกับตัวเองและคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-d641748997c5e31ab4fffa328a3c117535dd924d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "In this lesson, we learned how to talk about ourselves and other people.",
      "file": "en-us-830f5e6213023de6284a46a8c5fd1b0e20549e7b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เราเรียนรู้การพูดกับคนอื่น และการพูดเกี่ยวกับคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-f2079a3b4b05bf74bc053a50f85b10de1d4a52c5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We learned to speak to someone and to talk about someone.",
      "file": "en-us-eed54de021bbd68efcf4894e57cef1f50ee9a7e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตอนนี้คุณสามารถพูดประโยคง่าย ๆ เกี่ยวกับตัวเองและคนอื่นได้แล้ว",
      "file": "th-th-b77f90a9e0c9b3f25af78d11fe2b979e98f355ed.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Now you can say simple things about yourself and others.",
      "file": "en-us-4b3e08636ad0aecd9a656b4cbf2392fa0f0a30e8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "และจำไว้: พระเจ้ารู้จักคุณตามชื่อ และคุณพิเศษ",
      "file": "th-th-cad2806613c822b0039e8bf6ac8ec5fb0c587ca9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "And remember: God knows you by name and you are special.",
      "file": "en-us-b2f5aed4f81d4be82fd27757e4256808d5f37d0a.mp3"
    }
  ]
}